{"tid":1434482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自從有狗吠記者會之後，就開始一大班人宣揚中計論","createTime":"2019-08-08T19:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:12:21.000Z","uid":133519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"67b539103573bd2affcf8be92bb0b0d518dc3c0a","tid":1434482,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:43:41.000Z","msg":"佢要搞你觀星筆都可以係武器啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一有記者會，就有人話無論做乜都會俾人口實，中計，咁同五年前有乜分別<br />\n<br />\n唔知班人係咪係鬼，而家記者會仲有記者圍攻班狗，班狗日日柒撚懵懵食甜筒都嘅樣，使閪驚咩，我哋仲應該wfc，冷處理，使閪理佢。<br />\n<br />\n就算大家做乜都好，我都一樣支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780eec050a09a7e30a986ee9b9f4536c34787934","tid":1434482,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T19:56:38.000Z","msg":"佢d計洗得就唔洗搞成咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太多疑心反而會玩死自己"},{"pid":"e1f35027c8f0d599e075552fafd8c1d78f5d5cba","tid":1434482,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T20:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af7d803ecc1a38c200917fd5e3f26617e8c45e5","tid":1434482,"uid":133519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}